Distribution. The type-locality is Pearl Harbor, south shore of Oahu, Hawaii (
Treadwell 1943
). Additional specimens were found at Paiko Lagoon (
Thomas 1973
;
Bailey-Brock 1987
), Hanauma Bay, and Kaimana beach, south shore, and at Kahuku, north shore of Oahu, Hawaii. This distribution indicates that
T. hawaiensis
is endemic to Oahu, Hawaii.
